1. We can use the value annotation with collections like List, Map, Set, properties
2. We have to use the add the below tag in the config.xml file

  <util:list list-class="java.util.Arraylist" id="temp">
    <value>Himachal</value>
    <value>Punjab</value>
    <value>Jammu</value>
    </util:list>

3. After that, we have to add the #{temp} with below annotation
  @value("#{temp}")
